<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This message is sent from a filler application to notify other applications that a new sterilization lot has been created. The information provided in the SLT segment describes the new sterilization lot that has been created by the filler application.</p>
</div>
